        "heading": "Take organisation to the next level",
        "text": "<p>With the brilliant range of storage options from Totally Tiffany, keeping your craft supplies organised has never been easier! With Buddy Bags designed specifically for ink pads, marker pens and more, storage trays for your paper crafting tools and innovative folders for your metal dies, you'll never be unorganised again!<\/p>",
